    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality E46 M3, a true driver\u2019s specification featuring the S54 high-revving straight-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing. This example is mechanically flawless: the rod bearings have been replaced, the rear subframe reinforced, and the VANOS system completely overhauled for peak volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain features a precise 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been subtly enhanced with Bilstein PSS10 coilovers for improved turn-in and damping response without compromising GT comfort. Zero paint meter deviations and no interior bolster wear; this is a turnkey collector-grade icon for the discerning enthusiast.",
