      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings; the factory paint protection film remains crystal clear. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new\u2014the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the buttons retain their original matte texture, and it still carries that subtle new-car scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at the flagship dealership, with a thick binder of records to prove it. The engine bay is spotless, the undercarriage is free of debris, and the tires are brand-new high-performance rubber. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
